data.description: **Assumable Loan at 2.75%!** Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own a home in Hunter’s Crossing conveniently located near everything Bastrop has to offer. This lovely two-story home offers four bedrooms, three full bathrooms, two living areas and two dining areas. Bright and open floor plan, large rooms with walk-in closets, one secondary bedroom down-stairs with a full bathroom right outside, primary bedroom upstairs with his and hers closets and two additional bedrooms, secondary bathroom and laundry room conveniently located upstairs too. Hunter’s Crossing offers residents a junior Olympic-sized pool, multiple athletic courts and fields, a fishing pond and hike and bike trails. Bastrop offers an array of cafes, shopping, nightlife, salons, galleries, and much more. Refrigerator conveys.
